      <title>日本央行政策转变后贝莱德大力宣传日本投资机会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/blackrock-touts-japan-investment-opportunities-after-boj-s-policy-shift</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝莱德亚太区主管苏珊·陈 (Susan Chan) 表示，由于货币政策转变和公司治理改革创造了机遇，日本已成为对全球投资者有吸引力的目的地。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/blackrock-touts-japan-investment-opportunities-after-boj-s-policy-shift</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 23:45:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
